name: r-modeldata
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.5.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-modeldata
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/modeldata_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/modeldata/modeldata_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f7b760c38d8a36993fadbb64bfbba52fb0e66156529839d0ae6f4ad032a6c79c

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-dplyr
    - r-purrr
    - r-rlang
    - r-tibble
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-dplyr
    - r-purrr
    - r-rlang
    - r-tibble

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('modeldata')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('modeldata')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/tidymodels/modeldata
  license: MIT
  summary: Data sets used for demonstrating or testing model-related packages are contained in this package.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - philip-khor
